## ğŸ” RDD â†”ï¸ DataFrame Conversion

### ğŸ”¹ RDD to DataFrame

```python
rdd = spark.sparkContext.parallelize([(1, "Alice"), (2, "Bob")])
df = rdd.toDF(["id", "name"])
df.show()
```

---

### ğŸ”¹ DataFrame to RDD

```python
df = spark.createDataFrame([(1, "Alice"), (2, "Bob")], ["id", "name"])
rdd = df.rdd
print(rdd.collect())
```
